
2014-11-11  Andreas Grapentin  <andreas@grapentin.org>

	* asparagus.exp: reorganized imports and added custom step example
	* example/example-test.exp: updated to new format (removed \\'s)
	* lib/feedback.tcl: coloured output, taking output strings from global
	state variables improving log quality
	* lib/globals.tcl: added for reference of global variables
	* steps/default.tcl: added new steps for return code checking and
	output capture, changed the way steps work to standalone functions for
	'given', 'when', 'then' and 'and' and improved failure state checking
	* steps/dispatcher.tcl: added interface to add steps to the testsuite,
	added more generic string dispatching

